where
  a not in (1) and a not in (2) and a not in (3) and a not in (4) and a not in (5) and a not in (6) and a not in (7) and a not in (8)
  and a not in (9) and a not in (10) and a not in (11) and a not in (12) and a not in (13) and a not in (14) and a not in (15) and a not in (16)
  and a not in (17) and a not in (18) and a not in (19) and a not in (20) and a not in (21) and a not in (22) and a not in (23) and a not in (24)
  and a not in (25) and a not in (26) and a not in (27) and a not in (28) and a not in (29) and a not in (30) and a not in (31) and a not in (32)
  and a not in (33) and a not in (34) and a not in (35) and a not in (36) and a not in (37) and a not in (38) and a not in (39) and a not in (40)
  and a not in (41) and a not in (42) and a not in (43) and a not in (44) and a not in (45) and a not in (46) and a not in (47) and a not in (48)
  and a not in (49) and a not in (50) and a not in (51) and a not in (52) and a not in (53) and a not in (54) and a not in (55) and a not in (56)
  and a not in (57) and a not in (58) and a not in (59) and a not in (60) and a not in (61) and a not in (62) and a not in (63) and a not in (64)
;

